All kinds of UNIX scripts and DOS batch files:

 configure   - configure makefiles (sets library paths etc)
 makeall     - compiles and builds all OMNeT++ sources
 makeall.bat - makeall's DOS version (BC3.1)
 makemake    - create makefile for a simulation
 convert     - upgrade old OMNeT++ sources
 splitvec    - split an output vector file to separate vectors
 splitvec.bat- splitvec's DOS version
 all2unix    - convert all text files from DOS to Unix
 dos2unix    - convert text files to Unix
 gcc.c       - a hack to 'emulate' gcc on AIX
 seedtool.cc - generates seeds for random number generators
 readme      - this file
 prephtml, makedist, install.bat, pack.bat - used during development

--VA
